### Compare SQLx, Diesel, and SeaORM adapter cache behavior
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/query/users/42/orm-comparison
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ttl_ms": 5000,
  "tags": ["users", "orm-comparison"],
  "loader_delay_ms": 10,
  "flow_id": "orm-comparison-flow"
}

### Scenario runner: golden path
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scenario": "golden-path",
  "flow_id": "manual-golden",
  "reset": true
}

### List committed scenario files
GET {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/files

### Parsed scenario catalog with document and suite metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/catalog

### Run committed YAML scenario file
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/file/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "golden-path.yaml",
  "format": "yaml"
}

### Run committed regression suite file
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/suite/file/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "regression-suite.json"
}

### Run inline scenario suite
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/scenarios/suite/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "manual-inline-suite",
  "reset_between": true,
  "entries": [
    {
      "name": "named ttl",
      "scenario": "ttl"
    },
    {
      "name": "committed json",
      "file": "golden-path.json",
      "format": "json"
    }
  ]
}

